  {
    "uuid": "75cc546b-2af2-52fc-88db-813142c23cbe",
    "entry": "下拍",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "かはく",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "downbeat",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "指揮者のタクトが鋭く下拍を刻んだ瞬間、ホルンの咆哮がホールの静寂を鮮やかに切り裂いた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「リズムが後ろに倒れてるよ。もっと下拍に重みを乗せて、足の裏でしっかり地面を踏み込んで！」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼はメトロノームのように正確な下拍を刻み続け、即興演奏に走るメンバーたちの屋台骨を支えた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
